title: Beat the Internet with John Robins
overview: John Robins hosts the quiz show where contestants try to finish sentences based on some of the internet's most popular search terms.Can five contestants predict some of the most common â€˜autocompletes' and survive to the final round?John is ably assisted by fact-master Sunil Patel, who explains just why we search for the things we do.It's the only quiz show where humans supply the questions and robots supply the answers, and where you're only ever one round away from being deleted from the game.
